description: Shawarma & Falafel Palace is where you’ll find mouthwatering Mediterranean cuisine that is sure to please your palate. This cool blue truck is serving up all the classic favorites, like falafel wraps, beef & chicken shawarma, creamy hummus, and crisp Greek salads. For one of the tastiest mobile meals you’ll ever eat, come on out and try Shawarma & Falafel Palace!
name: Shawarma and Falafel Palace
